      skos:note "The team has formally switched its retrospective format from start-stop-continue to the Velociraptor format, which structures each retro around three nautical-metaphor sections: Sailed (what went well), Stalled (what slowed progress), and Capsized (what went wrong). The change took effect last sprint." .

